Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "teacher1@test.com",
  "password": "Teacher123!"
}

### 9. Try to get all accounts with Teacher token (Should fail - unauthorized)
### (Replace {teacherToken} with token from step 8)
GET http://localhost:5166/api/Account/all
Authorization: Bearer {teacherToken}

### 10. Try to get all accounts without token (Should fail - unauthorized)
GET http://localhost:5166/api/Account/all

### Expected Results:
### - Step 7: Should return list of teachers and students (not admin)
### - Step 9: Should return 403 Forbidden (Role not authorized)
### - Step 10: Should return 401 Unauthorized (No token)